<subSubSection box="[199,1240,546,573]" pageId="27" pageNumber="214" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,150,608]" box="[199,1240,546,573]" pageId="27" pageNumber="214">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,546,572]" pageId="27" pageNumber="214">Etymology.</emphasis>
Superior process of genital cup claw-shaped (
<emphasis box="[852,975,546,572]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="214">unguiculus</emphasis>
= diminutive of Claw).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
